Comparison table:

Method              Best for
─────────────────────────────────────
Jenkins Credentials → Jenkins pipelines
AWS Secrets Manager → AWS services, rotation
AWS Parameter Store → Simple key/value, cheaper
Kubernetes Secrets  → EKS workloads
HashiCorp Vault     → Enterprise, multi-cloud
Environment vars    → Never for production ❌
